title: Grateful Dead Live at Sports Palace on 1981-10-19
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw-> Franklin's Tower, Mama Tried-> Mexicali Blues, Loser, CC Rider, Tennessee Jed, Passenger, Althea, Let It Grow

Set 2

Scarlet Begonias-> Fire On The Mountain-> Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Drums-> Spanish Jam-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Sugar Magnolia, E: Don't Ease Me In

reviews.review_text: Might as well try Very enjoyable matrix here..nice Jack Straw>Franklins to open the show and a solid 1st set to follow..you can feel the energy from the crowd..a hot 2nd set to follow that just flows right to a bouncy Don't Ease Me In to cap a wonderful night in Spain~~Forever Grateful>Forever Dead..GIVE IT A WHIRL MY FRIENDS

This kicks butt Great sound for an excellent show - one of my top ten wish I coulda been there shows, SPAIN!
Those folks know how to party, and Barcelona is a fantastic city.
Awesome show Great up.  Thank you.
